# Frontend (Mist & Haven Living)

Stack: Next.js App Router, React, Tailwind v4, shadcn/ui, Framer Motion (`FadeUp`, `StaggerChildren`).

## Four states (required on user-facing surfaces)

| State | Pattern |
|-------|---------|
| Loading | Route: `app/(site)/loading.tsx` / `app/admin/loading.tsx`. Actions: disabled button + "Saving…" / skeleton. |
| Empty | `EmptyState` — message + next action, never a blank grid. |
| Error | Route: `error.tsx` with reset. Forms/API: inline `AdminMessage` or field errors. |
| Success | Confirm outcome (saved, sent) before clearing loading. |

```tsx
// ❌ Only happy path
{categories.map(...)}

// ✅ Empty handled
{categories.length === 0 ? <EmptyState ... /> : <CategoryGrid ... />}
```

## Design tokens (`app/globals.css`)

Use Tailwind theme classes — `text-taupe`, `bg-pearl`, `border-hairline`, `text-sage-deep`, `font-display`, `py-section-mobile`, `btn-solid` / `btn-ghost`. No new hardcoded hex in components.

## Layout & a11y

- Mobile-first; tap targets ≥ 44px on interactive controls.
- Meaningful `aria-label` / `role="status"` on loading and empty regions.
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` (see globals.css); prefer existing motion helpers over new heavy animation.

## Admin client editors

Use `AdminMessage` + `AdminSaveButton` from `AdminShell`; show upload progress on `ImageUploadField` / `PdfUploadField`.
